'''Exhibition Day''' was a day where [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawans]] and initiates of any age performed exercises while [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Masters]] watched. These exercises included [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|exercises]], balance, endurance, climbing, jumping and swimming. Sometimes they were split into teams of two or four. It was play but it was also serious. The [[Jedi Temple Apprentice Tournament]] often took place on or around this day.<ref name="YDR">''[[Yoda: Dark Rendezvous]]''</ref>

